Rachael is age 15 in form two at St. Mathews Sesinia School. She has four other siblings and has learned through a lot of difficulties. The father is not employed and depends on micro-contacts, which at times are not easy to come by. Rachael is a hardworking student mich determined to excel in life. She has a lot of financial challenges not even able to raise over 1000 KSH for school fees on termly basis. Our school has tried to hold on to her just to assist her in completing her education for has to realise her full potential. If assisted Rachel is a girl who is very promising. She really needs great support from sympathisers and well wishers.
